    {
      "instruction": "<p>Cut your<strong> naan[s]</strong> in half</p><p>Spread your<strong> mango chutney</strong> evenly over one side of the <strong>halved</strong> <strong>naan[s]</strong> and top with your <strong>ground cumin</strong> and <strong>grated cheese</strong></p><p>Top with your <strong>nigella seeds</strong>, <strong>sliced red chilli</strong> (can't handle the heat? Go easy!) and <strong>half</strong> the <strong>sliced</strong> <strong>spring onion</strong> (save the rest for later!)</p><p>Sandwich the <strong>halved</strong> <strong>naan[s]</strong> together</p>",
