    {
      "instruction": "<p>Chop your<strong> cherry tomatoes</strong> in half</p><p>Top, tail, peel and grate your<strong> carrot[s]</strong></p><p>Wash your <strong>salad</strong>, then pat it dry with kitchen paper</p>",
