    {
      "instruction": "<p>Combine your <strong>white wine vinegar</strong> with a drizzle of <strong>olive oil</strong> and a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and <strong>pepper</strong> in a bowl – this is your <strong>dressing</strong></p><p>Once the sweet potatoes are almost done, heat a large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick) with a drizzle of <strong>vegetable oil</strong> over a medium heat</p>",
