    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once hot, add the <strong>naan sandwich[es]</strong> and cover with a smaller pan</p><p>Add a heavy weight (e.g. several tins) to the top pan and cook for 2-3 min per side, checking occasionally – this is your <strong>cheddar, chilli & mango naan toastie</strong></p><p>Tip: You may need to do this in batches!</p>",
