      "instruction": "<p>While the toastie[s] is cooking, add the <strong>salad</strong>, <strong>grated carrot</strong>, <strong>halved cherry tomatoes</strong>,<strong> roast sweet potato</strong> and <strong>remaining sliced spring onion</strong> to the bowl with the <strong>dressing</strong></p><p>Gently toss everything together – this is your<strong> salad</strong></p>",
